subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
lead_paragraph: Jeff Gordon denied Brad Keselowski’s bid for a perfect weekend with a late run in the last practice at Loudon, N.H., that put him at the top of the chart at 135.357 miles per hour.
